# Cost Discipline Rule

## Intent
Maintain the project as a low-to-zero cost MVP during its initial phase.

## Guidelines
- Choose free tiers for hosting (Streamlit Cloud), database (Supabase/Neon Postgres), and compute (GitHub Actions).
- Do not introduce paid services (e.g., Confluent Kafka, advanced Mapbox APIs, paid observability) unless absolutely required by scale.
- Keep ingestion frequency within API rate limits and free-tier GitHub Action limits.
- Favor simplicity and built-in tools (like Streamlit's native map) over complex paid alternatives.